  "prompt": "What universities does Viad recruit new grads from? What majors are they looking for?",
  "response": "Viad, a company that provides various services including event and experiential marketing, typically recruits new graduates from a range of universities and majors that align with their business needs. While specific universities may vary by year and location, companies like Viad often target well-known institutions with strong programs in relevant fields.\n\nIn terms of majors, Viad generally looks for candidates with backgrounds in:\n\n- Marketing\n- Business Administration\n- Event Management\n- Communications\n- Hospitality Management\n- Graphic Design\n- Project Management\n- Public Relations\n\nFor the most accurate and current information regarding Viad's recruitment practices, including specific universities and majors, it's best to check their official careers page or reach out directly to their HR department. Networking events, career fairs, and university job boards can also provide insights into their recruitment activities.",
